INSURANCE

If you previously installed the 890.210 or 890.344 unmanaged package or have done this step before, you're all set. If not, create and activate Lightning record pages manually.

Create the Lightning record pages that apply to Insurance and Insurance Industries Extension orgs.

Activate the Lightning record pages when you save them for the first time or later using the Activation button.
